{
  "stem": "8359.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were not allowed into the camp-- only the ones in uniform.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Do you understand what I'm--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was a military--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in other words, we-- we didn't have any fears that something could happen to us from the people on the outside, you know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, who knows what they were capable?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were capable of doing anything and everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were afraid of everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm still afraid of a lot of things, believe me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had a relationship with a man that-- he was a mechanic.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was fixing the machines when something went wrong.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think he was a-- what they call a Social Democrat in those days.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he really-- he was-- he really took his life in his own hands, because he was so good to us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He-- he, you know, got to know a few of us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you-- you can't trust-- I mean, we wouldn't have squealed, but some people just-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They can-- it's not that you can't trust them, but they can say things that they may be sorry for, you know what I'm-- And he would get behind the machine, where he-- nobody could see him.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he would speak to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He would be telling us how the war's, you know, going.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he would try and bring us some food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then if he heard that somebody was sick and needed a medication, he tried to get it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We loved him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I forgot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you know what we called him?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We couldn't refer to him by name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because if we were overhead, you know, he would have been-- we called him Uncle.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we called him in Polish.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
